res]]''\n| Herself/Thelma Harper (celebrity panelist)\n| 45 episodes\n|-\n| 2006\u20132011\n| ''[[Hannah Montana]]''\n| [[Ruthie Stewart|Ruthie \"Mamaw\" Stewart]]\n| 5 episodes\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''[[RuPaul's Drag Race All Stars]]''\n| Herself/Thelma Harper \n| 1 episode\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Celebrity Family Feud]]''\n| Herself\n| 1 episode\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Great News]]''\n| Angie Deltaliano\n| 4 episodes\n|-\n| 2018&ndash;19\n| ''[[The Cool Kids (TV series)|The Cool Kids]]''\n| Margaret\n| Starring role\n|}\n\n==Discography==\n\n===Albums===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n! colspan=\"2\"| Chart Positions\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Catalog #\n|-\n! style=\"width:50px;\"| <small>[[Billboard 200|U.S.]]</small>\n! style=\"width:50px;\"| <small>Can.</small>\n|-\n| 1973\n| ''[[The Night the Lights Went Out in Georgia (Vicki Lawrence album)|The Night the Lights Went Out in Georgia]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 51\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 31\n| Bell 1120\n|-\n| 1974\n| ''Ships in the Night''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| SOSL10106\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''Newborn Woman''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| WindMill L26\n|}\n\n===Singles===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Song\n! colspan=\"8\"| Chart Positions\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n|- style=\"font-size:smaller;\"\n! style=\"width:35px;\"| [[Billboard Hot 100|U.S.]]\n! style=\"width:35px;\"| [[Hot Adult Contemporary Tracks|U.S. AC]]\n! style=\"width:35px;\"| [[Hot Country Songs|U.S. Country]]\n! style=\"width:35px;\"| Can.\n! style=\"width:35px;\"| Can. AC\n! style=\"width:35px;\"| Can. Country\n! style=\"width:35px;\"| Australia\n! style=\"width:35px;\"| [[New Zealand Listener|NZ]]\n|-\n| 1969\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| \"And I'll Go\"<br /><small>b/w \"The Whole State Of Alabama\"</small>\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u