a banks on tourism to beat poverty|newspaper=[[The Guardian]]|location=London|date=6 January 2007|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2007/jan/07/rorycarroll.theobserver|accessdate=3 January 2015}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=cia>{{cite web|author=Central Intelligence Agency|authorlink=Central Intelligence Agency|title=The world factbook|publisher=Central Intelligence Agency|location=Washington, D.C.|year=2019|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=ciaexport>{{cite web|author=Central Intelligence Agency|authorlink=Central Intelligence Agency|title=World exports by country|work=The world factbook|publisher=Central Intelligence Agency|location=Washington, D.C.|year=2014|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/fields/2078.html#74|access-date=1 January 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120504222805/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/fields/2078.html#74|archive-date=4 May 2012|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=ciaexportgu>{{cite web|author=Central Intelligence Agency|authorlink=Central Intelligence Agency|title=Export partners of Guatemala|work=The world factbook|publisher=Central Intelligence Agency|location=Washington, D.C.|year=2014|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/fields/2050.html#gt}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Cuellar2013>{{cite news|last=Cuellar|first=M|title=Foreign direct investments and tourism up|newspaper=Channel 5 Belize|publisher=Great Belize Productions Ltd.|location=Belize|date=1 March 2013|url=http://edition.channel5belize.com/archives/82643|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref><ref name=handbook2013>{{cite book|author=IBP, Inc|title=Central America Economic Integration and Cooperation Handbook Volume 1 Strategic Information, Organizations and Programs|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=9AWWBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA8|year=2009|isbn=978-1-4387-4280-9|page=8}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Harvey2008>{{cite journal|last=Harvey|first=CA|last2=Komar|first